objectives.name: Bizevent type [com.easytrade.deposit.start] count
objectives.dqlQuery:
fetch bizevents
| filter event.type == "com.easytrade.deposit.start"
| fieldsAdd n = 1
| summarize sum(n) / $depositStartReferenceCount / $timeframeMinutes * $referenceTimeframeMinutes
